@QtBank.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5044

### Login request (Administrator)
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{QtBank.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@qtbank.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Weather Forecast (Authorized - requires Bearer token)
@authToken = {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}

GET {{QtBank.Api_HostAddress}}/api/weatherforecast?days=5
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Login request (Validation Error Demo)
POST {{QtBank.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "password": "short"
}
